{"tid":142892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對班波台垃圾好失望","createTime":"2017-03-04T07:27:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T00:16:11.000Z","uid":39800,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e519e4962f5a4b56de7981c6fd3eb6054df5648","tid":142892,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T07:27:39.000Z","msg":"今日，我見到波台有個po起左我底<br />\n原因係我喺站務台撐連巴，被視為盲撐狗<br />\n被人恥笑等等<br />\n我覺得好嬲，我記得我同班仆街講道理<br />\n我記得我講句高登可以賺錢，咁點解連登唔可以落廣告賺錢<br />\n但我只不過平時睇唔過班人假膠當撚狗姐<br />\n你地識我咩？知我份人係點咩？<br />\n一口就咬定我係小學雞盲撐撚？<br />\n未免太一竹竿打一船人掛？<br />\n我唔係嬲我俾人屌我係連尼狗，我都唔鐘意見到呢啲term<br />\n我係嬲無啦啦俾人攞出來做所謂&quot;公審&quot;<br />\n因為，我唔係盲撐撚<br />\n可能你地覺得咁樣係波台嘅作風，寧願殺錯無放過<br />\n但我接受唔到<br />\n我支持連登，但唔係盲撐撚<br />\n我鐘意呢度嘅文化，但有啲風氣實在不能接受<br />\n呢個應該係我喺度嘅最後一個po<br />\n但我目的唔係想講我唔再用LIHKG<br />\n而係我想波台班仆街收斂下，唔好再喺度搞破壞<br />\n因為LIHKG係個好論壇"},{"pid":"8eb415a7f2907a97e84a0bf9d14a75fbdbc06918","tid":142892,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T07:29:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">睇下會唔會有人俾你撚到先</span>"},{"pid":"3666e3d9dad37ac33719fc6ba41522958af6d7ab","tid":142892,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T07:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5aa962a1fcce7116a69a140baf346bc3511a6f","tid":142892,"uid":2022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T07:39:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb1c58a0432bb1194696a7ab29bcd18889100b4e","tid":142892,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T07:41:06.000Z","msg":"你班廢柴動氣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c008298f505def5f8eb7eaba1387f11873658f3","tid":142892,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T07:47:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你班廢柴動氣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇撚有錯"},{"pid":"24ad7b9468413709948b76dc0a0ec55f1cc7d11d","tid":142892,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T07:49:47.000Z","msg":"是撚旦啦<br />\n<br />\n今時今日通街打手其實唔上forum都無好大損失<br />\n<br />\n好老實平日睇youtube 片、直播都唔夠時間<br />\n<br />\n日日上到黎仲要睇d唔知咩居心嘅account 係度吹咩陰謀論、反對邊個撐邊個直情係浪費時間<br />\n<br />\n有得食好食啦，23都就立法，我就無興趣撐呢班垃圾香港人<br />\n<br />\n最多咪以後唔出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b537d1f2ed42d70b28fa344c5afd8be85d111c59","tid":142892,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T09:57:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca2be1fa34240247b4fd77c60425ac80cc3c0ff","tid":142892,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T10:13:34.000Z","msg":"小夫潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6780ad8898a98519bdf624808d6f41d2a6e8782","tid":142892,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T10:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ef6ec0f631557d63071e1e4efe501f3dc63b82","tid":142892,"uid":24814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:05:51.000Z","msg":"大家有大家玩咪好，高登以前好人流係班高質會員吸引番來，唔係喺人地果陣搞小動作番來，好心就死番自己地頭出下啲高質Post，唔好係道叫春"},{"pid":"499dd63bc812e3755566ace9b7c8d66d255939f4","tid":142892,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:19:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小夫潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aacf20352b85b7205550b7d16bbb2bd5160ff5aa","tid":142892,"